\begin_layout Itemize
\begin_inset Formula $E\left[\left(y-\bar{y}\right)^{2}\right]=E\left[\left\{ \sum_{i=1}^{n}\,\left(\frac{\partial f}{\partial x_{i}}\right)\left(x_{i}-\bar{x}_{i}\right)\right\} \cdot\left\{ \sum_{j=1}^{n}\,\left(\frac{\partial f}{\partial x_{j}}\right)\left(x_{j}-\bar{x}_{j}\right)\right\} \right]$
